results.name: Second-order linear recurrence sequence with a(n) = a(n-1) + a(n-2).
comment: a(0) = 407389224418, a(1) = 76343678551. This is a second-order linear recurrence sequence with a(0) and a(1) coprime that does not contain any primes. It was found by John Nicol in 1999.
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000
